{"tid":1866244,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱喺街屌到個冇戴罩嘅女仔跪喺度喊","createTime":"2020-02-06T15:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T12:51:06.000Z","uid":150100,"like":70,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"998c85b22ab76ff7750fc05fefde2459b7d26ac0","tid":1866244,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n頭先喺街見到個十幾廿歲嘅女仔罩都唔帶喺度行<br />\n於是我就行埋去問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:個女仔<br />\n<br />\n我：你做咩唔帶罩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個女仔：焗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：你知唔知咁做好危險㗎，害人又害已<br />\n個女仔：肺炎咋嘛，當年沙士我都冇戴罩啦<br />\n我：沙士還沙士，肺炎還肺炎，總之你唔帶罩呢，就好危險嘅<br />\n個女仔：我係唔中意戴呀~吹咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是我終於忍唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你同我跪喺度！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依一喝可以話係驚天地，泣鬼神<br />\n隔離個阿婆嚇到由個輪椅碌咗出馬路<br />\n個女仔嚇到即刻跪咗喺度<br />\n仲開始喊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我：屌你老母，口罩你就識戴，bra就唔肯戴<br />\n你唔戴bra成對波型出曬嚟不特止，粒的仲要現曬型，點搞呀小姐。啲司機一陣間掛住望炒車你點對得住人。同埋依家啲大陸佬落曬嚟，你咁樣好危險㗎，隨時失身之餘中埋肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路喊<br />\n最後我見佢話知錯喇就放過佢，陪佢一齊去買完罩再幫佢戴，返到屋企先除<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主做得好，依啲女唔屌唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地中華兒女係龍的傳人，唔駛帶罩"},{"pid":"d2ddd47dc0b4e11d6d787fe14fb15b49588adc72","tid":1866244,"uid":198800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好man"},{"pid":"c85a3a6cf39a639d702edbd4fdc52379a64654f5","tid":1866244,"uid":82829,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1